Industries


Insurance: Life & Health




Company Description


Texas Republic Capital Corp. operates as a life insurance holding company. The company’s primary objective is to capitalize a Texas-domiciled life insurance subsidiary through which it will underwrite and market life insurance products to Texas residents. Texas Republic Capital was founded on May 15, 2012 and is headquartered in Austin, TX.




